author: Bojan Pancevski
title: Sweden is forging its own pandemic path with most of the Western world under stay-at-home orders
description: Welcome to Sweden, the last holdout among the small number of Western countries to have taken a radically different approach to the coronavirus pandemic.
content:
The ski pistes are open, the restaurants are doing ample business, and the malls are awash with shoppers.
